      "value": "<p><em><strong>Detective Pursuit:</strong> 9th level</em></p>\n<p>Once on each of your turns, when you hit the target of your Critical Analysis with a melee weapon attack, you can make a Wisdom (Insight) check contested by the target's Charisma (Deception) check. If you win the contest, you deal an additional [[/r 1d8]] damage to the target, which is the same type as the weapon's damage</p>\n<p>This die increases to [[/r d10]] at 13th level and [[/r d12]] at 17th level.</p>",
